title: Episode 133: Matt Landsberg - How Small Business Owners Can Deal w/ The Corona Virus
description:
In this episode, Robbie interviews, Matt Landsberg, a successful franchise owner on how to prepare for the Corona Virus from both a business and mental health perspective to avoid fear, panic and financial ruin.

Show Notes:
Matt’s story of opening a Plato’s Closet franchise (01:30)

The advantages of opening a franchise (02:51)

What sort of returns and time/money commitment it took to near passive income.

Understanding your bias… are you a doomsday thinker or an optimist and how either mindsets can set you up for utter ruin…
